<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Rapport Médical #{{ dossier.id }}</title>
    <style>
        /* --- PAGE SETUP --- */
        @page { margin: 1cm; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #000;
            background: #fff;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        /* --- UTILS --- */
        .text-right { text-align: right; }
        .text-center { text-align: center; }
        .bold { font-weight: bold; }
        .uppercase { text-transform: uppercase; }
        .red { color: #b30000; }
        .small { font-size: 9px; color: #555; }
        
        /* --- HEADER --- */
        .header-table { width: 100%; border-bottom: 2px solid #000; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -1px; }
        .logo span { color: #b30000; }
        .hospital-info { font-size: 9px; color: #444; margin-top: 5px; }

        /* --- BARCODE SIMULATION --- */
        .barcode {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            background: #eee;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid #000;
        }

        /* --- SECTIONS --- */
        .section-box {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .section-header {
            background-color: #e0e0e0; /* Light Gray Medical Style */
            color: #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 10px;
        }
        .section-content { padding: 10px; }

        /* --- DATA TABLES --- */
        table.data { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        table.data td { vertical-align: top; padding: 4px 0; }
        .label { width: 35%; color: #444; font-size: 10px; }
        .value { width: 65%; font-weight: bold; font-size: 11px; }

        /* --- BMI BOX --- */
        .bmi-box {
            border: 1px dashed #444;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* --- VISUAL GAUGE (New) --- */
        .gauge-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #999;
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 8px;
            background: #eee;
        }
        .gauge-segment { float: left; height: 100%; }
        .marker {
            position: absolute;
            top: -3px;
            width: 2px;
            height: 18px;
            background-color: #000;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        .footer {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            font-size: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 5px;
            color: #777;
        }
        
        .signature-box {
            margin-top: 40px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .sig-line {
            width: 200px;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            margin-left: auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    {# --- HEADER --- #}
    <table class="header-table">
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 40%;">
                <div class="logo">BLOOD<span class="red">LINK</span></div>
                <div class="hospital-info">
                    CENTRE DE TRANSFUSION SANGUINE<br>
                    Service d'Hématologie & Dons<br>
                    Réf. Agrément: 2024-TN-BL
                </div>
            </td>
            
            {# ✅ QR CODE INTEGRATION #}
      {# Inside Header Table #}
<td style="width: 20%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
    {% if qrCode is defined and qrCode is not null %}
        <img src="{{ qrCode }}" alt="QR Code" style="width: 80px; height: auto;">
        <div style="font-size: 7px; color: #000; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;">
            SCANNER POUR<br>DONNÉES COMPLÈTES
        </div>
    {% endif %}
</td>

            <td style="width: 40%; text-align: right; vertical-align: bottom;">
                <div class="small uppercase">Identifiant Dossier</div>
                <div class="barcode">DL-{{ dossier.id }}-{{ "now"|date("Y") }}</div>
                <div class="small">Date du rapport : {{ "now"|date("d/m/Y H:i") }}</div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <h2 class="text-center uppercase" style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-decoration: underline;">
        Fiche Clinique & Biométique
    </h2>

    {# --- 1. IDENTIFICATION PATIENT --- #}
    <div class="section-box">
        <div class="section-header">1. Identification du Donneur</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <table class="data">
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">NOM & PRÉNOM :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.nom|upper }} {{ dossier.prenom|capitalize }}</td>
                    <td class="label">SEXE :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.sexe|upper }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">ÂGE :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.age }} Ans</td>
                    <td class="label">ID PATIENT :</td>
                    <td class="value">#{{ dossier.client ? dossier.client.id : 'N/A' }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">CONTACT URGENCE :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.contactUrgence }}</td>
                    <td class="label">GROUPE SANGUIN :</td>
                    <td class="value" style="font-size: 14px; border: 2px solid #000; padding: 2px 5px; display:inline-block;">
                        {{ dossier.typeSang }}
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# --- 2. EXAMEN CLINIQUE (With BMI Logic) --- #}
    <div class="section-box">
        <div class="section-header">2. Constantes Vitales & Anthropométrie</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <table class="data">
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">POIDS (Kg) :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.poid }}</td>
                    <td class="label">TAILLE (cm) :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.taille }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">TEMPÉRATURE (°C) :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.temperature }}</td>
                    <td class="label">APTITUDE :</td>
                    <td class="value bold">
                        {% if dossier.temperature > 37.5 %}
                            <span class="red">REJET TEMPORAIRE (Fièvre)</span>
                        {% else %}
                            APTE AU DON
                        {% endif %}
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            {# BMI CALCULATION LOGIC #}
            {% set heightM = dossier.taille / 100 %}
            {% if heightM > 0 %}
                {% set bmiVal = (dossier.poid / (heightM * heightM)) %}
                {% set interpretation = 'Normal' %}
                
                {% if bmiVal < 18.5 %} {% set interpretation = 'Insuffisance Pondérale' %}
                {% elseif bmiVal >= 25 and bmiVal < 30 %} {% set interpretation = 'Surpoids' %}
                {% elseif bmiVal >= 30 %} {% set interpretation = 'Obésité' %}
                {% endif %}

                <div class="bmi-box">
                    <table style="width: 100%;">
                        <tr>
                            <td width="30%"><strong>IMC (Calculé) :</strong></td>
                            <td width="20%" style="font-size: 14px;">{{ bmiVal|number_format(2, '.', ',') }}</td>
                            <td width="50%">
                                <strong>Interprétation : </strong> 
                                <span style="text-transform: uppercase;">{{ interpretation }}</span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>

                    {# ✅ VISUAL BMI GAUGE #}
                    {# Calculate Position: Map BMI 15-45 to 0-100% #}
                    {% set gaugePercent = ((bmiVal - 15) / 30) * 100 %}
                    {% if gaugePercent < 0 %}{% set gaugePercent = 0 %}{% endif %}
                    {% if gaugePercent > 100 %}{% set gaugePercent = 100 %}{% endif %}

                    <div class="gauge-container">
                        {# Underweight (<18.5) approx 12% width #}
                        <div class="gauge-segment" style="width: 12%; background: #5bc0de;"></div>
                        {# Normal (18.5-25) approx 22% width #}
                        <div class="gauge-segment" style="width: 22%; background: #5cb85c;"></div>
                        {# Overweight (25-30) approx 17% width #}
                        <div class="gauge-segment" style="width: 17%; background: #f0ad4e;"></div>
                        {# Obese (>30) rest #}
                        <div class="gauge-segment" style="width: 49%; background: #d9534f;"></div>
                        
                        {# The Black Marker #}
                        <div class="marker" style="left: {{ gaugePercent }}%;"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="font-size: 8px; color: #777; margin-top: 3px; display: table; width: 100%;">
                        <div style="display: table-cell; width: 12%;">Maigre</div>
                        <div style="display: table-cell; width: 22%;">Normal</div>
                        <div style="display: table-cell; width: 17%;">Surpoids</div>
                        <div style="display: table-cell;">Obésité</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>

    {# --- 3. DÉTAILS DU PRÉLÈVEMENT --- #}
    <div class="section-box">
        <div class="section-header">3. Données Transfusionnelles</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            <table class="data">
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">RÉFÉRENCE DON :</td>
                    <td class="value">#{{ dossier.don ? dossier.don.id : '----' }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">TYPE DE PRÉLÈVEMENT :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.don ? dossier.don.typeDon|upper : 'NON SPÉCIFIÉ' }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="label">DATE DE L'ACTE :</td>
                    <td class="value">{{ dossier.don ? dossier.don.date|date('d/m/Y') : 'N/A' }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    {# --- SIGNATURE AREA --- #}
    <div class="signature-box">
        <table width="100%">
            <tr>
                <td width="50%" style="font-size: 10px; color: #555;">
                    <div style="border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 10px; width: 80%;">
                        <strong>OBSERVATIONS MÉDICALES :</strong><br><br><br><br>
                        R.A.S.
                    </div>
                </td>
                <td width="50%">
                    <div class="sig-line">
                        Validation Médecin<br>
                        <span style="font-size: 9px; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic;">Cachet & Signature</span>
                    </div>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    {# --- FOOTER --- #}
    <div class="footer">
        Document confidentiel soumis au secret médical - Loi n° 2024-BL - Ne pas laisser à la vue du public.<br>
        Généré automatiquement par le système BloodLink - Page 1/1
    </div>

</body>
</html>